snippet.title: Incolatus - Official Weapons Deep Dive Trailer | Women-Led Games x TGA 2024
snippet.description: Join game director Jane Fiona for a closer look at some of the girlypop guns (weapons) of Incolatus: Don't Stop, Girlypop! in this new trailer for upcoming Y2K girly-pop arena-style movement shooter where standing still is not an option. The faster you go, the more damage you deal and the more you heal! Just. Don’t. Stop. Moving.
